body_html:
There is more than one set of instructions for install at tensorflow.org, and it's not clear which you followed.

There are two for windows, here: https://www.tensorflow.org/install/install_windows

The anaconda install is community supported, so it is more appropriate to ask questions regarding it on stackoverflow. Including your exact sequence of installation actions may help someone to identify your problem.
